name: League of Legends statistics viewer
tagline: Built with jQuery, CSS3, HTML5, JavaScript, PHP, AJAX and Bootstrap.
body:
# League of Legends Stats viewer

Web app that using the API provided by Riot Games, displays data about the champions used.

Built with jQuery, CSS3, HTML5, JavaScript, PHP, AJAX and Bootstrap.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
